   450тЖТ/// A visitor for a [`Value`].
   451тЖТ///
   452тЖТ/// Also see [`Value`'s documentation on serialization]. Value visitors are a simple alternative
   453тЖТ/// to a more fully-featured serialization framework like `serde` or `sval`. A value visitor
   454тЖТ/// can differentiate primitive types through methods like [`VisitValue::visit_bool`] and
   455тЖТ/// [`VisitValue::visit_str`], but more complex types like maps and sequences
